TYPE: Test,
TARGET: Continuity path from power-supply negative terminal through each series module to the load-module return terminal,
DESCRIPTION: With the battery removed, use a continuity tester to trace the 0 V (return) conductor through the chain. Start at the negative terminal in the power-supply module and verify continuity to the two outgoing leads, then successively across each module’s 0 V in-to-out connection (control modules 1–8 and then the load module). Note at which module, if any, the continuity path is interrupted or shorted to the 12 V line.,
